        {
          "answer": "You know what, you are right. What do you suggest?",
          "result": {
            "type": "megamod:dialogue",
            "text": "Build a Flower Shop! The florist will grow and arrange beautiful flowers all around the colony. Happy citizens are productive citizens, and nothing brightens the day quite like a splash of color!",
